{"tid":2140271,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"費蘭托利斯(費托) 正式轉會曼城 2.1億簽藍月5年","createTime":"2020-08-05T01:27:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-05T03:46:52.000Z","uid":19552,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"03c96b91ca3673ccafde3b41c5972268ef24e2da","tid":2140271,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T01:27:00.000Z","msg":"曼城周二宣佈正式由華倫西亞羅致了年輕翼鋒費倫托利斯，雙方簽約五年。藍月未有透露合約的財務細節，惟據英國傳媒報道，費倫托利斯的轉會費為2,300萬歐元（約2.1億港元）。<br />\n<br />\n剛過去的球季，現年20歲的費倫托利斯各項賽事為華倫西亞上陣44場，取得6個入球和8次助攻。成為了曼城今夏第一簽的這名西班牙U21國腳，將會頂替利萊辛尼離隊加盟拜仁慕尼黑後留下的空缺。<br />\n<br />\n費倫托利斯表示︰「很高興可以加盟曼城。所有球員都希望加入進攻球隊，而曼城是世界足壇其中一支最進取的球隊。」<br />\n<br />\n曼城在剛結束的英超球季取得第二名，落後冠軍利物浦18分，但該隊贏得了英格蘭聯賽盃，今季亦仍然在爭逐歐聯，周五將與主場迎戰皇家馬德里，進行歐聯16強次回合賽事。首回合曼城以2:1領先。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/Bzwu9aulEsK7k0RTGPLUr3Y5g8w=/802x451/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/GGAPA7YGG5AY5MV2QOF5VIE27U.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FBzwu9aulEsK7k0RTGPLUr3Y5g8w%3D%2F802x451%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FGGAPA7YGG5AY5MV2QOF5VIE27U.jpg&h=a9acfc08&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3bbe28ca9ac3b08b4bc71b18a0f28c483c8104cf","tid":2140271,"uid":29929,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T01:40:27.000Z","msg":"你老尾改d似足你個人咁低質"},{"pid":"af8aca54ba164be20b33afdd13161d1381bb59f5","tid":2140271,"uid":59546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T03:07:57.000Z","msg":"一單新聞fake兩個位 高汁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49de44d6414820c38ecb6750e81fb5ebd94a7232","tid":2140271,"uid":2216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T03:19:55.000Z","msg":"呢個唔係吹到好勁嘅咩？？？<br />\n點解只係21M???????"},{"pid":"1acd99a5d8a0229f6a52a79004f4768c3d67f688","tid":2140271,"uid":48609,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"reply